snippet.title: THE MÜLL LITTORAL | 2017 | RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Follow either of the links below to purchase the game!
https://gamejolt.com/games/Themulllittoral/252586
https://librarium-studios.itch.io/themulllittoral

This is a game about anxiety, and the hero's journey to treat it.
It is made entirely with traditionally drawn assets, and nearly everything in the game was done by one person.

I sincerely hope you enjoy the experience of The Müll Littoral.

http://www.librariumstudios.com
